org.botblock.javabotblockapi.requests

Class GetListAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.botblock.javabotblockapi.requests.GetListAction

  • public class GetListAction
extends Object
    Class used to perform GET actions on the /api/lists and /api/lists/:id endpoints.

    GET requests are cached for 2 minutes unless disabled through GetListAction(true).

    Since:
    5.0.0

      • GetListAction

        public GetListAction(boolean disableCache)
        Constructor to get the instance of GetListAction.
        Use this if you want to disable the caching of the GET requests.
        We do not recommend this without own caching/ratelimiting.
        Parameters:
        disableCache - Whether or not to disable caching. true means caching gets disabled!
